data.description: Your Relaxing Country Getaway! **COME and SEE** this elegant Georgian manor on over 5 acres, surrounded by rolling farmland. Custom built in 2000, this stunning home boasts over 12,600 TOTAL sqft. Just renovated with refinished original hardwoods and brand new carpeting throughout. New granite kitchen countertops and a bright and sunny breakfast room leading to an enormous outdoor patio. The formal dining room and living room both feature a brick fire place and plenty of natural light. Downstairs mother-in-law suite. Massive upstairs master bedroom en suite with a walk in closet. West wing has a two room suite with a private bathroom as well. 5 bedrooms upstairs total. Stairs to the 1400+ sqft attic with walkable floors. Unfinished 2699 sqft basement roughed-in to be a separate apartment!  Attached garage, outdoor shed on property and ample garden space. Close to 64, easy commute to Williamsburg, VA Beach and Richmond, but still feels far away from the world. A private vacation house, a grand family home, or an amazing investment in hospitality or as a B&B on a historical property~ zoning already allows! Enjoy the freedom of this country getaway with Virginia sunsets and no HOA!
